<section id="asuka-mari" class="level2">
<h2>Asuka &amp; Mari</h2>
<figure>
<img height="1160" src="../images/eva/2010-crc/mari-asuka.jpg" title="http://1.bp.blogspot.com/_iCnzf-y60cc/TLrxQFgEWUI/AAAAAAAACbY/o8xPfOsou70/s1600/mari-asuka.jpg" width="1600"/>
</figure>
<p>See Hideaki Anno‚Äôs interview, <a href="#part-2">part 2</a> &amp; <a href="#part-3">part 3</a>:</p>
<blockquote>
<p>‚Ä¶At this point, there was a development where, during the fight with the falling angel, Mari and Asuka are present in the [Unit-02] entry plug together‚Ä¶By the draft of February 15 2008, draft 13a, I had the idea that ‚ÄúMari‚Äôs appearances following the pre-title sequence will come sooner, be more numerous, and be more impressive. To that end, Mari will take charge of the battlefield during the fight against the falling angel, riding with Asuka, who hates the situation, in the entry plug [of Unit-02]‚Äù. Then Mari covers [Â∫á„ÅÜ] for Asuka, but a wound she received during the pre-title sequence grows worse, so she is hospitalized until she reappears again in the last scene. That was the plan, but it didn‚Äôt work out.</p>
</blockquote>
